### BlastRadius — REST API Test Requests
### Use with VS Code REST Client or IntelliJ HTTP Client
### ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

@base = http://localhost:8080
@contentType = application/json

### ─── Variables (fill after login) ─────────────────────────
@token = PUT_JWT_TOKEN_HERE
@scanId = 1
@componentId = 1


### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
### AUTH
### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

### [1] Register a new user
POST {{base}}/api/auth/register
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "username": "admin",
  "password": "password123",
  "role": "ADMIN"
}

---

### [2] Register a regular user
POST {{base}}/api/auth/register
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "username": "developer",
  "password": "dev12345",
  "role": "USER"
}

---

### [3] Login (copy accessToken and set @token above)
POST {{base}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "username": "admin",
  "password": "password123"
}

---

### [4] Refresh token
POST {{base}}/api/auth/refresh
X-Refresh-Token: PUT_REFRESH_TOKEN_HERE

---


### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
### REPOSITORY SCANNER
### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

### [5] Scan a local git repository
# Replace the repoPath with a valid local Java project directory.
POST {{base}}/api/repositories/scan
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "repoPath": "/Users/deepawasthi/Downloads/BlastRadius",
  "forceRescan": false
}

---

### [6] List all scans
GET {{base}}/api/repositories/scans
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

---

### [7] Get specific scan status
GET {{base}}/api/repositories/scans/{{scanId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

---


### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
### DISCOVERY
### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

### [8] Get all APIs (controllers) for a scan
GET {{base}}/api/apis?scanId={{scanId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

---

### [9] Get all services
GET {{base}}/api/services?scanId={{scanId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

---

### [10] Get all entities
GET {{base}}/api/entities?scanId={{scanId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

---

### [11] Get all tables
GET {{base}}/api/tables?scanId={{scanId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

---

### [12] Get all components (no type filter)
GET {{base}}/api/components?scanId={{scanId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

---

### [13] Get components filtered by type
GET {{base}}/api/components?scanId={{scanId}}&type=REPOSITORY
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

---

### [14] Search components by name
GET {{base}}/api/search?query=user&scanId={{scanId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

---


### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
### DEPENDENCY ANALYSIS
### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

### [15] Get all dependency relationships
GET {{base}}/api/dependencies?scanId={{scanId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

---

### [16] Impact analysis for a component
GET {{base}}/api/impact-analysis?scanId={{scanId}}&componentId={{componentId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

---

### [17] Get circular dependencies (node IDs in cycles)
GET {{base}}/api/circular-dependencies?scanId={{scanId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

---

### [18] Get dead code components
GET {{base}}/api/dead-code?scanId={{scanId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

---


### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
### RISK ANALYSIS
### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

### [19] Get top risk components
GET {{base}}/api/risk?scanId={{scanId}}&limit=20
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

---


### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
### REPORTS
### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

### [20] Dependency report (all relationships)
GET {{base}}/api/reports/dependency?scanId={{scanId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

---

### [21] Risk report (components ordered by risk)
GET {{base}}/api/reports/risk?scanId={{scanId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

---

### [22] Architecture drift report (violations)
GET {{base}}/api/reports/architecture?scanId={{scanId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

---


### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
### DASHBOARD
### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

### [23] Get aggregated dashboard metrics
GET {{base}}/api/dashboard?scanId={{scanId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

---


### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
### GIT INTELLIGENCE
### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

### [24] Analyze git history
GET {{base}}/api/git/analyze?repoPath=/Users/deepawasthi/Downloads/BlastRadius
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

---


### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
### EXPORTS
### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

### [25] Export full graph as JSON
GET {{base}}/api/export/json?scanId={{scanId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

---

### [26] Export components as CSV
GET {{base}}/api/export/csv/components?scanId={{scanId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

---

### [27] Export relationships as CSV
GET {{base}}/api/export/csv/relationships?scanId={{scanId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

---

### [28] Export risk report as PDF
GET {{base}}/api/export/pdf/risk?scanId={{scanId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

---


